## 公式

### FORM-001

- model_id: `MOD-003`
- expression_or_pseudocode: `For window w, return_w = close_last / close_start(w) - 1.0. 1m uses latest date minus 31 calendar days, 3m uses latest date minus 93 calendar days, and 10d uses the point at len(points)-11. If the start point is missing or start close is 0, output None.`
- evidence_refs: `EVID-SER-FORMULA-REGISTRY, EVID-SER-MODEL-EXTRACTION`

### FORM-002

- model_id: `MOD-003`
- expression_or_pseudocode: `Iterate daily closes, track running peak, compute drawdown = (peak.close - point.close) / peak.close. Max drawdown is the largest drawdown. Recovery time is days from worst trough until a later close >= worst peak, else days from trough to latest point. Recent drawdown uses last 7 points as (max_recent_close - latest_close) / max_recent_close.`
- evidence_refs: `EVID-SER-FORMULA-REGISTRY, EVID-SER-MODEL-EXTRACTION`

### FORM-003

- model_id: `MOD-001`
- expression_or_pseudocode: `total_score = data_score + timeliness_score + source_score + return_score + risk_score + executable_score. data_score = max(0,25 - 8*missing_count). timeliness_score = 15 if max(missing_nav_days,missing_holding_days) <= 2 else 0. source_score = 15 if official_source_count >= 2 and no conflict, 7.5 if official_source_count >= 1 and no conflict, else 0. return_score = 15*(benchmark_wins/6). risk_score starts 0, becomes max(0,20 - 20*max_drawdown) when max_drawdown < 0.40, and is capped to min(risk_score,5) when recovery_time_days >= 365. executable_score = 10 unless rule missing or subscription/redemption/fee schedule fields are unavailable or closed.`
- evidence_refs: `EVID-SER-FORMULA-REGISTRY, EVID-SER-MODEL-EXTRACTION`

### FORM-004

- model_id: `MOD-001`
- expression_or_pseudocode: `Grade decision table: if score >= 85 then Action-Ready; else if score >= 70 then Watch; else if score >= 55 then Manual Review; else Block.`
- evidence_refs: `EVID-SER-FORMULA-REGISTRY, EVID-SER-MODEL-EXTRACTION`

### FORM-005

- model_id: `MOD-001`
- expression_or_pseudocode: `Precise gate order: excluded or conservative -> Block/Block. max_drawdown >= 0.40 -> Block/Clear/manual_review. recovery_time_days >= 365 -> Block if return_score < 7.5 or any missing else Manual Review, action Manual Review. stale_days > 2 -> Manual Review. conflict_flag -> Manual Review. official_source_count < 2 -> cap Action-Ready to Watch and action Pause New. fallback_aggregated -> cap Action-Ready to Watch and action Pause New. executable_score == 0 -> cap Action-Ready to Watch and action Pause New. return_score == 0 -> Reduce. Action-Ready -> Increase. Watch -> Maintain.`
- evidence_refs: `EVID-SER-FORMULA-REGISTRY, EVID-SER-MODEL-EXTRACTION`

### FORM-006

- model_id: `MOD-001`
- expression_or_pseudocode: `benchmark_wins counts, for each window in 1m,3m,10d, one win if candidate return > Shanghai Composite return when Shanghai value exists, and one win if candidate return > S&P 500 return when S&P value exists. Equal values are not wins. Missing candidate return skips the window. return_score = 15 * benchmark_wins / 6.`
- evidence_refs: `EVID-SER-FORMULA-REGISTRY, EVID-SER-MODEL-EXTRACTION`

### FORM-007

- model_id: `MOD-002`
- expression_or_pseudocode: `Eligible rows are rows where score.grade != Block. Sort key is (int(score.manual_review_required), candidate_index default 1000000, -score.total_score, candidate.asset_code). Return first limit rows, default limit 5.`
- evidence_refs: `EVID-SER-FORMULA-REGISTRY, EVID-SER-MODEL-EXTRACTION`

### FORM-008

- model_id: `MOD-002`
- expression_or_pseudocode: `For each ranked Top5 item at zero-based index i, serenity_base = 0.82^i. confidence = clamp(score.total_score/100,0,1). confidence_multiplier = 0.85 + 0.15*confidence. raw_weight = serenity_base*confidence_multiplier. Normalize raw weights to sum 1. Cap each normalized weight at 0.30. Normalize capped weights again to sum 1.`
- evidence_refs: `EVID-SER-FORMULA-REGISTRY, EVID-SER-MODEL-EXTRACTION`

### FORM-009

- model_id: `MOD-002`
- expression_or_pseudocode: `deviation = target_weight - current_weight. If grade is Block, return score action/trigger. If manual_review_required, return Manual Review. If abs(deviation) <= 0.01, return Maintain. If deviation > 0, return Increase for Action-Ready else Pause New. If deviation < -0.01, return Reduce.`
- evidence_refs: `EVID-SER-FORMULA-REGISTRY, EVID-SER-MODEL-EXTRACTION`

### FORM-010

- model_id: `MOD-004`
- expression_or_pseudocode: `For each compare_type in same_day_previous, previous_day, previous_week, previous_month, choose the latest eligible success/pass business-day base run. change_rate = len(new_assets union removed_assets)/max(len(current_top5),1). Alert if change_rate > 0.20, new_assets count >= 1, replacement_count >= 2, or max_key_field_sigma > 1.0.`
- evidence_refs: `EVID-SER-FORMULA-REGISTRY, EVID-SER-MODEL-EXTRACTION`

### FORM-011

- model_id: `MOD-004`
- expression_or_pseudocode: `Deviation event triggers when abs(deviation) > 0.01. Single-position overexpansion checks last 5 R-slot runs and increments consecutive count while current_weight - target_weight > 0.01; alert when consecutive > 2.`
- evidence_refs: `EVID-SER-FORMULA-REGISTRY, EVID-SER-MODEL-EXTRACTION`

### FORM-012

- model_id: `MOD-005`
- expression_or_pseudocode: `A due slot exists only on Beijing business days by default and when abs(current Beijing time - scheduled slot time) <= tolerance_minutes, default 3. Slots are R1 08:30 through R10 17:30 Beijing. scheduler_tick skips duplicate slot/date unless allow_duplicate is true. automation_tick forces dry-run when preflight blocks.`
- evidence_refs: `EVID-SER-FORMULA-REGISTRY, EVID-SER-MODEL-EXTRACTION`

